      "questionText": "Which of the following compounds will form significant amount of meta product during mono-nitration\nreaction? ",
      "options": [
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l7ymwbrq/82dc1f63-d6c3-444e-b67f-1e8021b3b5a2/53843360-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymwbrr.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l7ymwbrq/82dc1f63-d6c3-444e-b67f-1e8021b3b5a2/53843360-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymwbrr.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2017 (Offline) Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 239 English Option 1\">",
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l7ymwvrf/406c3803-2b70-4d16-aa3b-9a364bf8e13f/62f599b0-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymwvrg.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l7ymwvrf/406c3803-2b70-4d16-aa3b-9a364bf8e13f/62f599b0-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymwvrg.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2017 (Offline) Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 239 English Option 2\">",
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l7ymxctv/85b32517-3ff1-4e53-a0a3-0c260bf6908f/7024ff40-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymxctw.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l7ymxctv/85b32517-3ff1-4e53-a0a3-0c260bf6908f/7024ff40-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymxctw.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2017 (Offline) Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 239 English Option 3\">",
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l7ymxu5d/953f415f-672e-47bb-83a2-e9cabf806bed/7d85d510-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymxu5e.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l7ymxu5d/953f415f-672e-47bb-83a2-e9cabf806bed/7d85d510-3287-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7ymxu5e.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2017 (Offline) Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 239 English Option 4\">"
