      "id": "1ldu0t1mv",
      "questionNumber": 10,
      "questionText": "<p>Match List I with List II</p>\n<p><style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-c3ow{border-color:inherit;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-7btt{border-color:inherit;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-0pky{border-color:inherit;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\" style=\"undefined;table-layout: fixed; width: 691px\">\n<colgroup>\n<col style=\"width: 50px\">\n<col style=\"width: 271px\">\n<col style=\"width: 45px\">\n<col style=\"width: 325px\">\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\">List I<br>Isomeric pairs</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\">List II<br>Type of isomers</th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">A.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Propanamine and N-Methylethanamine</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">I.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Metamers</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">B.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Hexan-2-one and Hexan-3-one</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">II.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Positional isomers</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">C.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Ethanamide and Hydroxyethanimine</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">III.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Functional isomers</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">D.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">o-nitrophenol and p-nitrophenol</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">IV.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">Tautomers</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></p>\n<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below :</p>",
