      "solution": "<p>A. Propanamine&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; N–Methylethanamine </p><p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ledtqgv2/bdcd6c28-0f60-4bef-9003-046012f5ac72/1e83c6f0-b1ab-11ed-afb4-c9dda1bdb882/file-1ledtqgv3.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ledtqgv2/bdcd6c28-0f60-4bef-9003-046012f5ac72/1e83c6f0-b1ab-11ed-afb4-c9dda1bdb882/file-1ledtqgv3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 25th January Evening Shift Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 97 English Explanation 1\"></p>\n<p>B. Hexan–2–one &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Hexan–3–one </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ledtsuec/5e890023-8f57-4c47-99dc-b6b3f6641214/60969a40-b1ab-11ed-8e7a-cdae5879fb93/file-1ledtsued.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ledtsuec/5e890023-8f57-4c47-99dc-b6b3f6641214/60969a40-b1ab-11ed-8e7a-cdae5879fb93/file-1ledtsued.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 25th January Evening Shift Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 97 English Explanation 2\"></p>\n<p>C. Ethanamide &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Hydroxyethanimine </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ledtwkvv/dd03c611-7273-46bb-8a7e-6f6a85350be9/c879e8b0-b1ab-11ed-8e7a-cdae5879fb93/file-1ledtwkvw.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ledtwkvv/dd03c611-7273-46bb-8a7e-6f6a85350be9/c879e8b0-b1ab-11ed-8e7a-cdae5879fb93/file-1ledtwkvw.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 25th January Evening Shift Chemistry - Compounds Containing Nitrogen Question 97 English Explanation 3\"></p>\n<p>D. o–Nitrophenol &nbs